snippet.title: Arcade Archives NEOGEO: OverTop - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a re-release of the NEOGEO version of OverTop, developed by ADK

Arcade Archives (C) Hamster Corporation
NEOGEO, OverTop (C) SNK

ACA NEOGEO release is also available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4 and Windows 10
